On the anniversary of his inauguration, Trump is flying to the World Economic Forum in Davos â€” an annual gathering of the global elite â€” where he may see many of the billionaires he has surrounded himself with during his first year back in the White House.  Trump had campaigned on lowering the cost of living, painting himself as a populist while serving fries at a McDonald's drive-thru.
